  "descriptionParagraphs": [
    "The Cheat Code from SHARPEYE Surfboards delivers the world's fastest surfboard developed to offer High Volume Performance in small-sized conditions.",
    "A tuned-up, up-volumed performance shortboard. The Cheat Code features a forgiving boxy rail that minimizes rail catches in full / flat sections and sub-par conditions. The bottom contour features a medium single concave that ends between the fins ending with a flat exit. These concaves combine with a flat entry rocker that flows seamlessly into a flat exit rocker, providing an instant burst of speed from take-off with exceptional control, drive and carry in small-sized conditions.",
    "We recommend riding this board 2-4 inches shorter than your regular shortboard and adding a touch of width and thickness."
